e going to say get a hamster because they have never had or even heard of a gerbil before two years ago i had never heard of gerbil either here is my story i went to the pet store to get specifically a hamster i was almost broke because i had spent like all my money on the cage and supplies i had like bucks and was hoping the hamsters were fairly cheap when i got there i realized that all the hamsters were and above just my luck i was so dissapointed then the store clerk let me know that they had gerbils on sale for i didn't know what it was she showed me them and they were all awake playing together i thought they were super cute and decided i wanted one i picked one out and brought him home i'm so glad that i did'nt have enough money for a hamster that day because happy my gerbil is the best pet i ever had i found out that gerbils like to live in pairs or more so i got him a male gerbil friend its now been two years with him and autumn my second gerbil i really hope you get to experience the joy of owning a pet gerbil they are the best rodents to have in my opinion good luck with your decision this site will help you learn more about them http www abcgerbils com Guinea pig Fancy rat Domestic rabbit Cat Meriones unguiculatus House Mouse Ferret Shaggy dog story Avenue Q Gerbil Sin City Social rule Rodent About a Boy One Tree Hill (TV series) Chinchilla Gaia Online Rat The Fairly OddParents Knots Landing Friends W.I.T.C.H. Current teachings of Prem Rawat The Ashlee Simpson Show EastEnders Pet Ron Weasley Dog Nocturnal animal New York Giants Pok__mon Live! Recurring South Park characters $ale of the Century The Life and Times of Juniper Lee Brown Rat Cro Muroidea The Young Ones (TV series) Sleeping Murder Spidey Super Stories Episodes of Lost (Season 1) Days of our Lives The Catcher in the Rye Little Britain Pet skunk 2000 Australian Grand Prix Scenes from a Memory Grand Theft Auto: San Andreas Dog training Calvin and Hobbes The Star Wars Holiday Special Similarities 